{"tid":1447252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣布”警你老母”係新一代侮辱詞語","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:56:49.000Z","uid":58794,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6a0ccc2f3d040117c63f8a88679f8f1fac842255","tid":1447252,"uid":58794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;警你老母&rdquo;正式成為新一代侮辱字，代替屌你老母，支拿，死全家，所以中英美法日韓所有粗口.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家以後好嬲要鬧人用警你老母就得嫁啦，個個人已經比你鬧到賤個地底泥，比屎更廢，畜生，垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n以後就用警你老母流芳百世，令香港永遠記得2019年，香港警察既所作所為。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班黑警唔洗置身事外，唔係你阿頭，唔係你個team，你地無得割蓆，以後做黑警就要好好保護你自己老母，我地將來直到永永遠遠都會提你娘親。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原諒我小學雞，但我真係好嬲好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591fdfd0db389fd07795c1af606b82c6203c4349","tid":1447252,"uid":58794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"aa73ff4e8782753d72a0d6bdd217a3763a7e351d","tid":1447252,"uid":58794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"3adecc1263ec62b34ca47979ad04858f2b7aa241","tid":1447252,"uid":58794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:44.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c3f5782e17b7a611c18b76f16b04d258043a7af8","tid":1447252,"uid":58794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:59.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"df9bdb9cef20c106b0781bbb24de9da53db2e743","tid":1447252,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:44:07.000Z","msg":"班狗有